2026-03-27 15:29:34.248 | INFO     | request_id - 1 | app.agent.nodes.generate_sql:generate_sql:35 - 生成SQL结果：SELECT 
    dp.brand,
    dp.product_name,
    SUM(fo.order_quantity) AS total_quantity
FROM dim_product dp
JOIN fact_order fo ON dp.product_id = fo.product_id
GROUP BY dp.brand, dp.product_name
